              <span class="faq-toggle"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12"><path d="M6 1v10M1 6h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg></span>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Google Analytics 4 replaced Universal Analytics on July 1, 2023. GA4 uses event-based tracking instead of session-based measurement, has a redesigned interface, and includes built-in machine learning for predictive metrics and attribution.</p></div></div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
